name: Paycorp
overview:
Paycorp is an Australian company with head quarters in Sydney. Paycorp provides payment solutions to help organisations become PCI compliant, consolidate payment collection methods and improve efficiencies in managing receivables.

Paycorp is certified as Level 1 PCI DSS Compliant Service Provider and has been working with the standard since it’s release in 2004.

The Paycorp system was originally developed for, and under the supervision of banks who mandated that security, authenticity and privacy of their transactions was beyond question.

Paycorp has been providing Internet related products and services since 1996, initially providing Internet Services specialising in high bandwidth, to small and medium sized businesses. The company extended its operations to hardware, networking, IVR solutions, professional services and business software development for the payments industry.

Today Paycorp processes over AUD $7 billion in payments annually and supports over 50,000 business clients both directly and indirectly including enterprises and financial insitutions.
